I am a 23-year-old singer-songwriter of French, Czech & German origins. I play the guitar, the piano, the Irish whistle, the harp, and I love to dance. My life goal is to make people feel fulfilled and inspire them through my music, and to create soundtracks for movies. I post my own original songs on my channel as well as covers. It's a difficult path to follow, as it is tough to get recognition online nowadays without paid promotion. I'm planning to release an album this year with many songs, but for this I would need your support. If you have a moment, please check out one of my videos and tell me what you think. snippet.textDisplay: I am having an anxiety attack right now, and I think it is triggered by this song. I have a handful of people to reach out for, but I can't. I feel helpless having these thoughts-- that I am sick and something within me, the sadness that eats up my whole being will be contagious and eat my loved ones the same way. I wanna be alone not because I want to, but because that's the only way they won't get hurt the same way it did to me. I can't even send a message to a close friend about  this. I wanna be free from this. I wanna be loved, and feel love like how normal people do.
